De_Crane (copywrite 2007)
Map created by: Luke Reznick (aka)-n2

This is a map I created for fun. It's a competitive map with a solid layout. 
Hope you guys enjoy.

Map is Using HDR and ColorCorrection Turn those on for better image quality.

Map completion in 55 man hours (not counting compile times)

Special thanks for support from the community.

Custom things inbedded in the BSP.

1.soundscape.manifest
2.soundscape.crane
3.crane.raw (colorcorrection)
4.de_crane.nav
5.de_crane.txt
6.Crane Radar
7.Crane music (easter-egg)
8.Custom Credit Textures
